        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 3. Dorsal view of the head of A. the holotype of Corydoras bethanae, MUSM 69403, female, 51.2 mm SL., showing the gap (yellow arrow) between body stripe and mask-like blotch, and B. Corydoras arcuatus, MNRJ 51069, 47.8 mm SL, showing the continuous stripe on region posterior to eye. Photo A. by Nemo Martin, and B. by Bruno Ferreira. Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4620762/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4620768>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 6. Live coloration of paratypes of Corydoras bethanae, BMNH 2017.5.25.1-21, showing A. female, and B. male. Fin coloration affected by background colors. Arrows indicate gap in arc-stripe around the suture between neurocranium. Photos by Steven Grant." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4620768/files/figure.png" .

